WEBVTT

00:00.440 --> 00:01.320
Don't listen to your sister

00:01.600 --> 00:02.480
If you're unhappy

00:02.480 --> 00:03.280
In the army

00:03.560 --> 00:04.880
I'll submit a memorial to His Majesty

00:05.080 --> 00:05.920
To have you transferred back

00:06.440 --> 00:07.760
So you can stay by your sister's side

00:08.160 --> 00:09.200
So she won't worry

00:11.160 --> 00:12.840
Then I'd still like to stay in the army

00:13.320 --> 00:13.880
In the future

00:13.880 --> 00:15.880
I still need to help brother-in-law with the northern expedition

00:18.840 --> 00:19.320
Right

00:20.440 --> 00:21.520
Almost forgot the important matter
